{"tid":1599274,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【12月實施】中國手機上網要先通過人臉識別","createTime":"2019-09-28T01:42:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T01:42:59.000Z","uid":53379,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"720b7ef07333f382a75f4401b1da837f6078e021","tid":1599274,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T01:42:59.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">【12月實施】中國手機上網要先通過人臉識別</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】工信部加入人臉識別作電話實名認證。<br />\n<br />\n工信部要求電訊公司12月開始，在實體管道全面實施人臉識別技術措施，對比一致後才可辦理入網手續，確保電話入網人證一致，防範倒賣及轉售電話卡，以及用戶在不知情的情況下辦理入網手續。<br />\n<br />\n工信部文件未有列明持有一卡兩號，或在香港申請內地電話卡的香港人是否需要配合措施，部分內地及香港電訊商表示，暫時未收到相關通知並不了解情況。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/finance/player?newsId=364279&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D364279%26refer%3D&d=%2F9qUFN9YWCJnPZyZgWzOj2ipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=0ff49822\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D364279%26refer%3D&h=6f87e4a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/finance/player?newsId=364279&amp;refer=</a>"}]}